        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Megophrys ancrae referred specimens from Changlang district, Arunachal Pradesh state, India: (a). adult male (SDBDU 2009.727: SVL 42.5 mm) in life; (b). adult male (SDBDU 2009.730: SVL 43.0 mm) in life; (c). adult male (SDBDU 2009.727) in preservation, ventral view showing hands with expanded digit tips; (d). adult males (SDBDU 2009.727, left & SDBDU 2009.730, right) in preservation, ventral view showing variation in markings." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4608907/files/figure.png" .

